<h2>A RESTful Service for Church Events.</h2>

<p>
This REST service is not intended for use in a web browser. It provides a mechanism
for interrogating the backend website database in order to provide XML formatted
information for use by client applications.
</p>

<p>
To see the information returned by this service then the "view source" option
should be used in any modern browser to examine the structure of the XML responses.
</p>

<p>
This release merely provides enquiry access to Church events. Further
development will provide further abilities for read only enquiries.
</p>

<p>
The future intention is to support the updating and creation of Church events
via a similar interface with appropriate security mechanisms.
</p>

